{% extends 'front_base.html.twig' %}

{% block body %}
<main>
	<h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center my-4 mt-12">
		Pixel Fusion<br>
		A small company with huge ambitions
	</h1>

	<section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
		<div class="container px-5 py-12 mx-auto flex flex-wrap">

			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-4 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 font-bold mb-4">About Us</h2>

				<p class="mb-4">Pixel Fusion was founded in 2022 by a group of friends who shared a love for video games
					and digital art. They noticed a gap in the market for high-quality digital assets for video game
					developers, and set out to create a platform where developers could find everything they need to
					bring their games to life.</p>

				<p class="mb-4">Our team is made up of experienced developers, designers, and artists who are passionate
					about creating the best digital assets for video games. We believe that every game should have
					access to high-quality assets, regardless of the size or budget of the development team.</p>

				<p class="mb-4">At Pixel Fusion, we're committed to providing our customers with the best possible
					experience. We strive to make our platform user-friendly and easy to navigate, and we're always
					looking for ways to improve.</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Our Story</h2>

				<p class="mb-4">It all started when our founder, John, was working on a small indie game with his
					friends. They had a great idea for a game, but they struggled to find high-quality assets that fit
					their vision. After spending hours searching for the right assets, they realized that there was a
					real need for a platform that offered a wide variety of assets for game developers.</p>

				<p class="mb-4">John enlisted the help of his friends, Sarah and Mike, who had experience in digital art
					and game development, respectively. Together, they set out to create Pixel Fusion, a platform that
					would offer a wide variety of digital assets for game developers of all levels.</p>

				<p class="mb-4">After months of hard work, Pixel Fusion was born. Our platform offers everything from 2D
					and 3D assets to sound effects and music, all created by our talented team of artists and
					developers.</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Our Mission</h2>

				<p class="mb-4">Our mission at Pixel Fusion is to provide game developers with the best possible digital
					assets, at an affordable price. We believe that every game deserves to look and sound its best, and
					we're committed to helping developers bring their visions to life.</p>

				<p class="mb-4">We're passionate about video games and digital art, and we're constantly looking for
					ways to improve our platform and create new and exciting assets. We're dedicated to providing our
					customers with a top-notch experience, and we're always here to help if you have any questions or
					concerns.</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Contact Us</h2>

				<p class="mb-4">If you have any questions or feedback, we'd love to hear from you. You can reach us by
					email at
					<a href="mailto:contact@Pixel Fusion.com"
						class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700">contact@pixelfusion.com</a>, or by filling out the
					contact form on our <a href={{ path('front_app_contact') }}
						class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700">Contact</a>
					page.
				</p>

				<p class="mb-4">Thanks for choosing Pixel Fusion for your digital asset needs. We can't wait to see what
					you create!</p>

			</div>
	</section>

</main>
{% endblock %}